fields.description: The ATX Jeans are amazingly comfortable for all-day wear. Made from premium stretch denim for an ideal fit that moves with you. Available colors are Black, Blue, and Yellow - pick your favorite wash to add some style to your routine.
fields.review_summary:
Here is a review summary of the customer reviews for ATX Jeans:

Pros:
- Very comfortable according to one reviewer. 

Cons: 
- Quality is questioned by some reviewers. Complaints include thin and flimsy denim, stitches coming undone quickly, holes developing in knees and thighs after only a few wears.
- Fit issues for one reviewer - too tight in thighs but loose in waist, sizing up did not fix the problem.  
- Itchy from day one according to one reviewer. Also started getting stains that did not come out and pilling got out of hand causing fabric to tear apart at seams within 3 months.
- Considered overpriced by one reviewer at over $100 for such poor construction quality that did not last more than a month of casual wear.  

In summary, while one reviewer found them very comfortable, other reviewers had major issues with the quality, fit, stitching and durability of ATX Jeans - feeling they were not worth the price given how quickly they deteriorated or developed problems. Most reviewers would not recommend or purchase from ATX Jeans again.

fields.description: The Jordan Shoes are stylish, comfortable and made for the everyday wearer. Crafted with high quality rubber soles for excellent traction and support, these shoes will keep your feet feeling fresh all day. The breathable cotton-polyester upper in a 20:80 ratio keeps your feet cool whether you're playing basketball or running errands. With exceptional craftsmanship and durability, the Jordan Shoes are perfect for both athletic performance and casual style. Slip into a pair today and experience the iconic Jordan comfort and quality with every step.

The RXN skinny fit shirt is supremely comfy for all seasons. Made from breathable cotton, it moves with you for all-day wear. Designed for the modern man, this versatile top is your effortless everyday essential.

The coziest tee for your little one! Ugg Kids T Shirt is made of breathable cotton for all-day comfort. Its skinny fit is great for every activity while staying comfy and cool in any weather. A wardrobe staple as versatile as your kid!

fields.subject: Disappointed
fields.review: I was really disappointed by the quality of ATX Jeans. The denim felt extremely thin and flimsy. After only a few wears, the knees and thighs started developing holes. The stitching came undone quickly as well. They weren't very flattering either - too tight in the thighs but loose in the waist. Even sizing up didn't fix the issue. Worst of all, these jeans were over $100 which is unreasonable for such poor construction. I expect my jeans to last more than a month of casual wear. I definitely won't be buying from ATX Jeans again and don't recommend them to anyone seeking pants that are well-made or value for money.

fields.subject: Poor quality and uncomfortable
fields.review: These jeans felt itchy from day one. Then they started getting strange stains that did not come off despite multiple washes. Within 3 months pilling got completely out of hand and the fabric started tearing apart at the seams. Threw them out as they became unusable
